com.poesys.db.dao.query

Class QueryCacheListWithKeyList<T extends IDbDto>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.poesys.db.dao.query.QueryListWithKeyList<T>
      • com.poesys.db.dao.query.QueryCacheListWithKeyList<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of IDbDto to query
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    IQueryList<T>

    public class QueryCacheListWithKeyList<T extends IDbDto>
extends QueryListWithKeyList<T>
    An implementation of the IQueryList interface that implements the basic elements of a query of multiple objects including caching using a list of primary keys in an IN clause. The query method executes the query and retrieves the results, but it first gets the primary key and looks up the object in the cache and uses any object that already exists rather than creating a new one.
    Author:
    Robert J. Muller
